The test Directory contains the scripts and configration files to build and start the
docker images and containers needed to run the test forum.

test
├── build-all                          Bash script to pull every together
├── docker-compose.yaml                The Docker Compose file used by build-all
├── .env                               Environment declarations use in the buil
├── apache2-dockerfile                 )
├── mysql-Dockerfile                   ) Docker files for apache, mysql and php containers
├── php-Dockerfile                     )
├── etc                                ) the etc config file copied into the containers
│   ├── httpd
│   │   ├── extra
│   │   │   ├── HTTPtoHTTPS.conf
│   │   │   └── test-ssl.conf
│   │   └── httpd.conf
│   ├── mysql
│   │   └── mysql
│   │       ├── conf.d
│   │       │   ├── docker.cnf
│   │       │   └── mysql.cnf
│   │       ├── my.cnf
│   │       └── my.cnf.fallback
│   └── php
│       ├── php
│       │   └── php.ini
│       └── php-fpm.d
│           └── www.conf
└── .secrets                           The test.buildhub.org.uk certs used by apache
    ├── fullchain.pem
    └── privkey.pem

Enjoy!